sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer as 客户
    participant UI as BalanceView
    participant API as atm.js/http.js
    participant C as AccountController
    participant T as TokenManager
    participant S as AccountServiceImpl
    participant DB as BankCardMapper/AccountMapper
    Customer->>UI: 选择查询余额
    UI->>API: getBalance(sessionId)
    API->>C: GET /api/atm/accounts/balance
    C->>T: 校验 sessionId
    T-->>C: cardNo
    C->>S: getBalance(cardNo)
    S->>DB: 查询银行卡与账户
    DB-->>S: Account.balance
    S-->>C: BigDecimal balance
    C-->>API: Result<BalanceResponse>
    API-->>UI: balance
    UI-->>Customer: 展示余额

